---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About FinanzasClara" description="FinanzasClara: practical personal finance advice backed by data and real experience. Meet the author.">
  <section class="about">
    <div class="container about__inner">
      <h1>About FinanzasClara</h1>

      <div class="about-author">
        <h2>Vladys Z.</h2>
        <p class="author-subtitle">App Developer · Professional Chef · Personal Finance Enthusiast</p>
      </div>

      <p>I'm Vladys, an app developer and professional chef who learned personal finance the hard way — by making every mistake in the book first. After years of tracking budgets, cutting costs, and building savings systems, I started FinanzasClara to share what actually works.</p>

      <p><strong>FinanzasClara</strong> is about practical money advice for real people. No get-rich-quick schemes, no expensive courses — just tested strategies backed by data and personal experience.</p>

      <h2>Why This Blog?</h2>
      <p>As a developer, I approach money like code: find the bug, fix it, optimize. As a chef, I know that the best recipes (and budgets) are simple, repeatable, and satisfying. Every article here cites real studies, names specific tools, and gives you actionable steps — not vague advice.</p>

      <h2>My Promise</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Real data</strong> — Every claim comes with a source: studies, institutions, verified numbers</li>
        <li><strong>Zero products to sell</strong> — I don't promote expensive courses, apps, or financial products</li>
        <li><strong>Personal experience</strong> — I share what I've actually tried and what works</li>
        <li><strong>Free forever</strong> — All knowledge is free and accessible</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Also on YouTube</h2>
      <p>I post daily money tips on <a href="https://youtube.com/@FinanzasClara-l3w" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@FinanzasClara</a> — quick, actionable finance content backed by real numbers.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>vladys.z96@gmail.com</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about { padding: 3rem 0; }
  .about__inner { max-width: var(--content-width); }
  .about__lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .about-author { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .author-subtitle { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--color-text-light); margin-top: 0.25rem; }
  .about h2 { margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .about p { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.7; }
  .about ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .about li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
</style>
